    <briefdescription>
<para>QApplication subclass enforcing single-instance behavior via IPC. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Detects whether another instance with the same unique key is running and enables forwarding messages (e.g., command-line arguments) to it. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
